  "original_title": "\u0da9\u0dd3\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db1\u0ddc\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Lack of diesel hampers container transport",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "United Lanka Container Transport Vehicle Owners Association says that 90 percent of export container vehicles did not run today (7th).",
        "The association said that although there are nearly 6000 container transport vehicles, less than 500 are currently running.",
        "They mentioned that if an acceptable program is not presented to release diesel for container transport vehicles, there is a situation where all the container transport vehicles will stop running."
      ],
